    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that fits a tighter budget? This fair-condition vehicle is a solid everyday driver that gets you where you need to go! It does show some wear and tear \u2014 you'll notice cosmetic imperfections and signs of use inside and out \u2014 but the mechanicals are functional and it's ready for the road. If you're looking for practical transportation without paying mint-condition prices, this could be a great fit for you!",
